    {
        "class": "Implement",
        "text": "Now substitute A = 0, C = 0, and D = -B into (3):\n\u2003\u20030 + 2B + 0 - 2(-B) = 2B + 2B = 4B = 1\u2003\u27f9\u2003B = 1/4."
